Simple program to turn python lists into unicode tables.
Planning to add support for Restructured Text tables later.

Usage in python file.

Example output:

┌──────┬────────┬──────────────────────────┐
│ Foo  │  Bar   │           Quux           │
├──────┼────────┼──────────────────────────┤
│ Baz  │ Wubble │          Wobble          │
│ Baz  │ Wubble │          Wobble          │
│ Baz  │ Wubble │          Wobble          │
│ Baz  │ Wubble │          Wobble          │
│ Baz  │ Wubble │ WobbleWobbleWobbleWobble │
└──────┴────────┴──────────────────────────┘

